cast.overview: Super-assassin John Wick returns with a $14 million price tag on his head and an army of bounty-hunting killers on his trail. After killing a member of the shadowy international assassin’s guild, the High Table, John Wick is excommunicado, but the world’s most ruthless hit men and women await his every turn.
cast.title: John Wick: Chapter 3 - Parabellum

details.biography: Asia Kate Dillon was born on November 15, 1984 in Ithaca, New York, USA. They are known for playing Brandy Epps in Orange Is the New Black and Taylor Mason in Billions. Their role on Billions is the first gender non-binary character on American television. Dillon identifies as non-binary and uses singular they pronouns.
details.name: Asia Kate Dillon
